# iTerm2 Cheatsheet

## Enter Copy Mode
`cmd-shift-c`

## Exit Copy Mode
`Esc`, `q`, `Ctrl-C`, `Ctrl-G`

## toggle selection by character (visual mode)
`v`, `space`

## toggle line selection (visual-line mode)
`V`

## toggle rectangle selection (visual-block mode)
`ctrl-v`

## copy selection
`y`, `ctrl-k`
